<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>This notice confirms the approach to the Common Travel Area (CTA) arrangements and the associated rights and privileges of British and Irish citizens if the UK leaves the EU without a deal. It clarifies that British and Irish citizens are not required to take any action to protect their existing entitlements.</p>

<p>Mae’r hysbysiad hwn yn cadarnhau’r dull o ymdrin â’r trefniadau Ardal Deithio Gyffredin (CTA) a’r hawliau a breintiau cysylltiedig sydd gan ddinasyddion Prydeinig a Gwyddelig os bydd y Deyrnas Unedig yn gadael yr Undeb Ewropeaidd heb gytundeb. Mae’n egluro nad oes angen i ddinasyddion Prydeinig na Gwyddelig gymryd unrhyw gamau i ddiogelu eu hawliau presennol.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

